title: ROCKEFELLER CENTER

seo_description: From soaring views at Top of the Rock to NBC Studios tours and the iconic skating rink, Rockefeller Center offers an endless array of activities and events in a complex consisting of 19 buildings covering 22 acres between 48th Street and 51st Street.

From soaring views at Top of the Rock to NBC Studios tours and the iconic skating rink, Rockefeller Center offers an endless array of activities and events in a complex consisting of 19 buildings covering 22 acres between 48th Street and 51st Street.
